{"tid":1475523,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"談警察通例引內地網民質疑 王喜神回覆獲讚","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:05:29.000Z","uid":52621,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58699be6f64695d0c3e2dd23f55ed854d4150abf","tid":1475523,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"曾任識警員的王喜在Facebook談到PGO，亦即是警察通例。他在文中感慨︰「現職嘅，應該個個比我熟PGO，但鏡頭記錄到嘅行為，都同我記得嘅嗰本PGO裡面無嘅。」他提到「『執行法律賦予的權力時，可使用適當的武力。』&mdash; 《警察通例：使用武力的目的》未完㗎，後面重有一句，呢句先至係成個使用武力chapter嘅核心。『當目的已達到，應停止使用武力。』&mdash; 《警察通例：使用武力的原則》」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565869581_Ut-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565869581_Ut-1280w.png&h=0d4c282c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王喜又提到《警察通例》是藉著約束所有級別警察的言行、舉止，目的是要確保執法者擁有高尚道德及品格，防止廣泛又強大的法律權力落入道德或品格低劣的人手上，同時這通例非香港法例，對公眾無效，只適用於警察，卻對公眾的生命財產，發揮致為重要的功用，就是將壞人革職，杜絕公權力落入邪惡之手。<br />\n<br />\n有一名簡體字名字的網民留言問︰「偽君子，來發表一下在機場發生的事情」，王喜看過對方的Facebook個人簡介後，回應說︰「入藉美國，人在加州，美國國土，建立中華聯邦，即是，拋棄中國在先，背叛美國在後，你是那門子奸？」這個回覆令不少留言讚好，更令到對方至今亦未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565869790_WG-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565869790_WG-1280w.png&h=6e3d8381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gelekchodar/photos/a.456970247752745/2287600561356362/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgelekchodar%2Fphotos%2Fa.456970247752745%2F2287600561356362%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=00198d88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gelekchodar/photos/a.456970247752745/2287600561356362/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"9d878317cb4d9b2f067e5d13fa517c83a8d17ea6","tid":1475523,"uid":67325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"媽，好柒呀！"},{"pid":"1bd7416bf984a163ef693d90052f43cf32502136","tid":1475523,"uid":64816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3355cbc77d97c63c444da289ac6d38a73a84f1","tid":1475523,"uid":31094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"王喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e61aa88c0b733e86df687bc84fb9ba1be916ff6","tid":1475523,"uid":286792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90a4a7a614bf6dd451e69e59fc4609f5e7f0283f","tid":1475523,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dac56ff6c0bf8f07d29fc9681445f822d13b1394","tid":1475523,"uid":36701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"一針見血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ffd9658221100d054fd65f4df4dda5ee477174","tid":1475523,"uid":265739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:52:55.000Z","msg":"班狗嘅目的係殺死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d411756ce681af64b28214a63aab9889ccf8d1","tid":1475523,"uid":208270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"班支那人係咁，享受自由卻擁護中國"},{"pid":"db447a716bdb5e6feb3a8f6906eb15d793d51802","tid":1475523,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94d411756ce681af64b28214a63aab9889ccf8d1","tid":1475523,"uid":208270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"班支那人係咁，享受自由卻擁護中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"送佢返去"},{"pid":"35bbf0100038b707533d3f536798b7f7478ca04f","tid":1475523,"uid":227312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T1